在[[幾何學|幾何學]]中，'''維脊'''（'''Ridge'''）又稱為'''亞面'''（'''subfacet'''）<ref>N.W. Johnson, ''Geometries and Transformations'', (2018) {{ISBN|978-1-107-10340-5}} Chapter 11: ''Finite symmetry groups'', 11.1 Polytopes and Honeycombs, p.225</ref>是指[[幾何形狀|幾何形狀]]的組成元素中，比該幾何形狀所在維度少2個維度的元素{{#tag:ref|{{harvtxt|Matoušek|2002}}<ref name="m">{{citation|title=Lectures in Discrete Geometry|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=0N5RVe5lKQUC&pg=PA86|at=5.3 Faces of a Convex Polytope|volume=212|series=[[Graduate_Texts_in_Mathematics|Graduate Texts in Mathematics]]|publisher=Springer|year=2002|authorlink=Jiří Matoušek (mathematician)|first=Jiří|last=Matoušek|accessdate=2019-09-16|archive-date=2019-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190610095148/https://books.google.com/books?id=0N5RVe5lKQUC&pg=PA86|dead-url=no}}.</ref>, p. 87}}{{#tag:ref|{{harvtxt|Ziegler|1995}}<ref name="z">{{citation|first=Günter M.|last=Ziegler|authorlink=Günter M. Ziegler|title=Lectures on Polytopes|at=Definition 2.1|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=xd25TXSSUcgC&pg=PA51|volume=152|series=Graduate Texts in Mathematics|publisher=Springer|year=1995|accessdate=2019-09-16|archive-date=2019-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190612031449/https://books.google.com/books?id=xd25TXSSUcgC&pg=PA51|dead-url=no}}</ref>, p. 71}}，其可以視為幾何結構中，兩個或多個維面相交成的幾何結構。<ref>{{PolyCell |urlname=glossary.html#Ridge |title=Glossary for hyperspace: Ridge}}</ref>其可以視為多面體的頂點、邊、面中的'''邊'''在高維幾何結構的推廣。

== 多邊形的維脊 ==
[[多邊形|多邊形]]是一種[[二維|二維]]幾何結構<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20050212114016/http://members.aol.com/Polycell/what.html What Are Polyhedra?], with Greek Numerical Prefixes</ref>，因此其所對應的維脊即為其[[頂點_(幾何)|頂點]]。而在比[[多邊形|多邊形]]更低維度的幾何結構中，通常不會探討維脊以及其特性。

== 多面體的維脊 ==
[[多面體|多面體]]是一種三維幾何結構<ref>{{citation|title=Solid Geometry|first=Joseph P.|last=McCormack|publisher=D. Appleton-Century Company|year=1931|page=416}}</ref><ref>{{citation|title=Computational Geometry: Algorithms and Applications|last1=de Berg|first1=M.|last2=van Kreveld|first2=M.|last3=Overmars|first3=M.|author3-link=Mark Overmars|last4=Schwarzkopf|first4=O.|author4-link=Otfried Cheong|edition=2nd|publisher=Springer|year=2000|page=64}}</ref>，因此其所對應的維脊即為其稜。在特殊命名的高維結構[[維面|維面]]、維脊和維峰中，正好對應到了多面體的面、邊和頂點<ref name="g">{{citation|title=Convex Polytopes|first=Branko|last=Grünbaum|authorlink=Branko Grünbaum|page=17|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ISHO86XJ1CsC&pg=PA17|volume=221|edition=2nd|series=Graduate Texts in Mathematics|publisher=Springer|year=2003|accessdate=2019-09-16|archive-date=2013-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131031083447/http://books.google.com/books?id=ISHO86XJ1CsC&pg=PA17|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 高維多胞形的維脊 ==
